Place the peppers in an oven or on a barbecue and roast until they are s\
oft and charred Let the peppers rest in a paper bag for 10 minutes  allow\
ing the steam from hot peppers to loosen the charred skin Remove the pepp\
ers from the bag  and peel off the skin and discard Remove the seeds and \
cut into 1/4-inch strips In a large saucepan  heat the extra-virgin olive\
 oil and the garlic Add the capers  black olives  and pepper strips Cook \
 for a few minutes more  and season with salt Sprinkle with the parsley an\
 d bread crumbs  and stir well Remove the garlic  and let rest for 15 minu\
 tes before serving','Zia Franca's Roaste